    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the way u put that... it's like you actually get it. most people just tell me to \"be strong\" or \"it'll get better,\" but it won't. it literally won't. i feel like i'm just waiting for a break that's never coming. do you think it's wrong to just... stop trying to survive this?",
